<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 15:44:04 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>内外</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4bcd4258189</link><description>&lt;p&gt;内部外部。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Rain, a car rearview mirror, facade of a house." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a4bcd4258189.jpg" width="1125"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 15:44:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4b7feecf71b</link><description>&lt;p&gt;粉色与蓝绿色&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="The interior of a typical Norwegian wooden church from the 1830s, featuring doors in front of the pews, a two-storey gallery and a pulpit-altar (a characteristic Norwegian feature from the 19th century). The wooden walls and columns are painted teal, whilst the panelling and the walls of the two galleries are painted in a pink marble-effect finish. The columns in the nave and around the pulpit altar are also painted in a marble-effect finish (those around the altar in pink). A pale pink carpet runs from the entrance to the altar. A brass-coloured chandelier hangs from the ceiling. The church is one of the largest in the region and has a total of 700 seats … just to put that into perspective when compared with churches in other countries. " height="3648" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a4b7feecf71b.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 10:14:13 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>电量满格</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4ae42fc5ecf</link><description>&lt;p&gt;低电量转满电量&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A small black and white dog stretches out on her stomach in the sun, in a scrubby patch of grass and weeds. She’s staring at the ground like she’s dazed." height="2448" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jinx/6a4ae42fc5ecf.jpg" width="3264"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jinx.some.pics"&gt;@jinx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 23:09:39 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4a85bae93ee</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一棵橡树的大树枝上，一片橡树叶的小芽成为了焦点（本就该如此！）。光线如此戏剧化，吸引了我的目光。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="In the foreground, a large branch of an oak tree crosses the frame midway, horizontally. In the middle of the frame, on top of the branch, a little shoot of new oak leaves is bathed in a patch of sunlight like a spotlight, making it glow. The backdrop is dense foliage." height="1500" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/bsag/6a4a85bae93ee.webp" width="2000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://bsag.some.pics"&gt;@bsag&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 16:26:38 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>溪边旋花</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4a850d06c90</link><description>&lt;p&gt;小溪边的一些旋花。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A patch of white, trumpet shaped Convolvulus flowers in the sun, near to a stream which can just been seen in the shade at the top right. The flowers are pointing towards the sun. Some are fully open, others closed, twisted like furled umbrellas." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/bsag/6a4a850d06c90.webp" width="1500"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://bsag.some.pics"&gt;@bsag&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 16:23:44 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>